{"root":{"data":{"id":"dgkc0q93jsw0","created":1771645794589,"text":"高中地理必修二"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc2j47d1c0","created":1771645935784,"text":"第一章 人口","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc8rnsc140","created":1771646424567,"text":"人口的变化，既受自然条件和社会经济条件的影响，\n又对自然环境和社会经济有着重大作用。当今世界存在的\n资源、环境、发展等问题，往往都与人口问题直接关联。\n历史和现实都表明，人口的变化一定要与区域资源环境承\n载力相适应，与社会经济发展相协调。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc45ysor40","created":1771646063887,"text":"第一节 人口分布","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc952007c0","created":1771646453725,"text":"世界人口的分布","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkcb491i2g0","created":1771646608702,"text":"人类诞生以来，经过漫长的繁衍与迁徙，如今已分布\n在地球上除南极洲以外的所有大陆上。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcb61lzu80","created":1771646612606,"text":"世界上的人口分布很不均匀，\n有的地区人口稠密，有的地区则人口稀少。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcbb80m200","created":1771646623877,"text":"从全球来看，近 90% 的人口居住在北半球，尤其在北\n纬 10°—50°地带最为集中。从距离海洋远近来看，60% 左\n右的人口居住在离海岸 200 千米以内的沿海地区。从海拔\n来看，近 80% 的人口居住在海拔 500 米以下的低平地区。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcfm4fyps0","created":1771646961063,"text":"各大洲和地区的人口分布极不平衡，\n亚洲、非洲和拉丁美洲人口约占世界总人口的 85%。\n各国人口分布也不平衡，截至2021 年年底，世界上\n人口超过1亿的国家有中国、印度、美国、印度尼西\n亚、巴基斯坦、巴西、尼日利亚、孟加拉国、俄罗\n斯、墨西哥、日本、埃塞俄比亚、菲律宾、埃及等。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcbh7ai740","created":1771646636894,"text":"世界四大人口稠密区","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkcdb7azww0","created":1771646780563,"text":"世界古老的文明中心，人类在此聚居的历史悠久。","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkcbontkvs0","created":1771646653131,"text":"东亚","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkcbz4emcw0","created":1771646675902,"text":"我国东部","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcc1i5fxs0","created":1771646681087,"text":"朝鲜半岛","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcc59y80g0","created":1771646689298,"text":"日本中南部","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcc84aa740","created":1771646695486,"text":"...","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcbqgkdm00","created":1771646657046,"text":"南亚","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkcce0r30o0","created":1771646708333,"text":"印度","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkccfi1jaw0","created":1771646711555,"text":"巴基斯坦","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkccgrex480","created":1771646714298,"text":"孟加拉国","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkccjl6c340","created":1771646720452,"text":"斯里兰卡","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkccm6f7og0","created":1771646726090,"text":"...","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcdlb8j140","created":1771646802568,"text":"经济发达，人口大多聚居在城市。","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkcbs13nbc0","created":1771646660465,"text":"欧洲西部","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkcdvjhc0g0","created":1771646824835,"text":"英国","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcdyo1sk80","created":1771646831641,"text":"法国","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcdznqrps0","created":1771646833799,"text":"德国","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkce0ytgu00","created":1771646836646,"text":"荷兰","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkce3bvswo0","created":1771646841789,"text":"...","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcburk1kg0","created":1771646666418,"text":"北美东部","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkce7o4oo00","created":1771646851237,"text":"美国东部","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkcebgay5s0","created":1771646859471,"text":"加拿大东南部","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc9msir3k0","created":1771646492333,"text":"影响人口分布的因素","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkca7pswbk0","created":1771646537882,"text":"影响人口分布的因素可归纳为自然因素和人\n文因素两大类。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl4uvxwtiw0","created":1771727148975,"text":"自然因素","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc9tmlbr40","created":1771646507212,"text":"人类的生活和生产活动离不开自然环境。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl5rivlnc80","created":1771729706555,"text":"自然环境对人口分布的影响明显，其中气候、地形等自然因素对人口分布影响尤为重要","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl5y4xc4h40","created":1771730224734,"text":"适宜","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl5yahwfvk0","created":1771730236861,"text":"气候较为适宜的中、低纬度地区","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl5zwv7pdc0","created":1771730363920,"text":"地势低平地区","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl602itixs0","created":1771730376231,"text":"平原地区","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl60a3jws00","created":1771730392722,"text":"华北平原","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl60elfd540","created":1771730402510,"text":"长江中下游平原","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl60j0h4wo0","created":1771730412127,"text":"恒河平原","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl60uyts600","created":1771730438149,"text":"富有水源的地区","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl618kq0vk0","created":1771730467771,"text":"北美五大湖地区","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl61qzdlq80","created":1771730507839,"text":"塔里木盆地的绿洲","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl5y6ss2zs0","created":1771730228812,"text":"不适宜","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl5ybf5alc0","created":1771730238872,"text":"过于寒冷、干旱的地区","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl5yopkl540","created":1771730267800,"text":"高纬度地带","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl5yro3c8o0","created":1771730274241,"text":"干旱的沙漠，戈壁地区","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl5yzxr1540","created":1771730292239,"text":"过于湿热的地区","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl5z5cwas80","created":1771730304039,"text":"雨林地区","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc9vbzcrk0","created":1771646510924,"text":"人文因素","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl647j9nag0","created":1771730700599,"text":"在自然条件的基础上，人口分布作为一种社会现象，还受社会经济条件、发展历史等人文因素的制约。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl66zgdp0w0","created":1771730918102,"text":"人类社会发展的不同阶段，生产力水平不同，社会生产方式不同，人口分布的特点也不同。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6etzyaso0","created":1771731533138,"text":"农业社会以个体农业生产为主，人口主要分布在农业发达地区。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6f0ykai80","created":1771731548292,"text":"工业社会的生产力水平得到空前发展，工业占据主导地位，工业企业集中在城镇，导致人口向城镇聚集。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6f5ejqjs0","created":1771731557966,"text":"在一些工业发达的地区，形成了人口密集的城市带。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl68agu5pc0","created":1771731020439,"text":"人文影响因素","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl67k2be8g0","created":1771730962964,"text":"经济发展水平","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl691sh84g0","created":1771731079917,"text":"经济发展水平较高的地区，人口稠密","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl69ck8gcw0","created":1771731103362,"text":"我国东部地区","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl69fkgb3s0","created":1771731109905,"text":"美国东北部地区","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl69kb5pzk0","created":1771731120227,"text":"欧洲西部地区","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl67ldeisg0","created":1771730965811,"text":"历史因素","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6cfhzfdk0","created":1771731344849,"text":"历史较悠久的地区，人口稠密","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6cp7tg5k0","created":1771731366002,"text":"东亚，南亚的人口稠密区","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6czf1wio0","created":1771731388207,"text":"政治","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6d149u1s0","created":1771731391909,"text":"军事","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6d23ua7k0","created":1771731394059,"text":"文化","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6d3zcg3c0","created":1771731398141,"text":"...","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6db6ufxs0","created":1771731413832,"text":"世界人口的分布状况是自然、人文各因素综合作用的结果","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc49izh3s0","created":1771646071638,"text":"第二节 人口迁移","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6s8ryc6w0","created":1771732584041,"text":"什么是人口迁移","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6mib1qio0","created":1771732134601,"text":"我们把涉及人口居住地发生长期或永久改变的人口移动，称为人口迁移。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6mq8s0c80","created":1771732151878,"text":"种类"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6qo0wqcg0","created":1771732460505,"text":"国际人口迁移"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6qsp28m80","created":1771732470673,"text":"国内人口迁移"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6r7qp9m00","created":1771732503424,"text":"人口机械增长"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6rcxarc00","created":1771732514707,"text":"人口迁移使得某一区域的人口数量发生变化，这种人口数量的变化称为人口机械增长。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6rlrg5ko0","created":1771732533944,"text":"人口机械增长率"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6rrt55kw0","created":1771732547107,"text":"人口机械增长率：是指一定区域、一定时间内（通常为 1 年），净迁入人口占总人口的比例，又称人口净迁移率。"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6sgjl32w0","created":1771732600949,"text":"影响人口迁移的因素"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dglci5bz63s0","created":1771748719562,"text":"推拉理论"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dglcillfxc80","created":1771748754963,"text":"人口迁移的动力由迁出地的推力（排斥力）与迁入地的拉力（吸引力）共同构成。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgld0zw45ls0","created":1771750196638,"text":"概念","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dglcj3pdf140","created":1771748794383,"text":"迁出地的一种或多种不利因素所产生的推力，迫使人们迁出"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dglcuuic4s00","created":1771749714736,"text":"迁入地的一种或多种有利因素所形成的拉力，促使人们迁入"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgld0q7ir6g0","created":1771750175560,"text":"自然因素和人文因素都有可能成为人口迁移的推力因素或拉力因素，人口迁移正是这些因素综合作用的结果。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6t4cpe740","created":1771732652776,"text":"自然因素"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgq8dsx0ik00","created":1772244894423,"text":"地区之间自然环境的差异，以及自然环境的变化，对人口迁移有重要的影响。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgq8msnt5lk0","created":1772245599144,"text":"推力"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgq8my3tay80","created":1772245610995,"text":"拉力"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgq8n3yr9ls0","created":1772245623750,"text":"环境问题、自然灾害等对人口迁移产生巨大的推力。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6ta89m200","created":1771732665568,"text":"人文因素"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6sn0c8hk0","created":1771732615023,"text":"人口迁移的时空特点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgl6tgjzq5c0","created":1771732679338,"text":"国际人口迁移"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgl6tivv3w00","created":1771732684409,"text":"国内人口迁移"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc4c8nisw0","created":1771646077544,"text":"第三节 人口容量","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc4jed5i80","created":1771646093126,"text":"问题研究 如何看待农民工现象","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc38i28qg0","created":1771645991041,"text":"第二章 乡村和城镇","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc4si2fj40","created":1771646112941,"text":"第一节 乡村和城镇空间结构","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc50vmucw0","created":1771646131176,"text":"第二节 城镇化","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc542n8uw0","created":1771646138130,"text":"第三节 地域文化与城乡景观","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc5c30a1s0","created":1771646155566,"text":"问题研究 从市中心到郊区，你选择住哪里","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc3e3eggo0","created":1771646003215,"text":"第三章 产业区位因素","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc5sqq5u00","created":1771646191829,"text":"第一节 农业区位因素及其变化","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc5yp9wg00","created":1771646204802,"text":"第二节 工业区位因素及其变化","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc65vq2i00","created":1771646220429,"text":"第三节 服务业区位因素及其变化","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc6e4gpnc0","created":1771646238373,"text":"问题研究 实体商店何去何从","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc3lrugag0","created":1771646019931,"text":"第四章 交通运输布局与区域发展","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc6mmcu600","created":1771646256868,"text":"第一节 区域发展对交通运输布局的影响","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc6v8hnns0","created":1771646275621,"text":"第二节 交通运输布局对区域发展的影响","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc73atl940","created":1771646293176,"text":"问题研究 城市交通如何疏堵","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc3ueqtpk0","created":1771646038730,"text":"第五章 环境与发展","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc7hdle5c0","created":1771646323819,"text":"第一节 人类面临的主要环境问题","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc7rluviw0","created":1771646346086,"text":"第二节 走向人地协调——可持续发展","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc80tyieo0","created":1771646366167,"text":"第三节 中国国家发展战略举例","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc8a441540","created":1771646386372,"text":"问题探究 低碳食品知多少","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"snow","version":"1.4.43"}